## Location
src/tweethoarder/cli/export.py lines 337-345

## Risk
- Malicious URL with javascript: scheme could execute code
- URL containing quotes could break out of attribute

## Fix
Add URL validation function:
function isValidMediaUrl(url) {
  return url && (url.startsWith('https://pbs.twimg.com/') || url.startsWith('https://video.twimg.com/'));
}
Then wrap: if (isValidMediaUrl(url)) { ... } else { return ''; }
